    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vessels built or equipped to carry out salvage work: i.e. the retrieval of a sunken ship after the cargo has removed. Usually equipped with heavy duty pumps, lifting equipment, winches and cables.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
